<p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #334155;">Hi <%= @user.name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #334155;">Someone requested a password reset for your account. Click the button below to choose a new password:</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px;">
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0f172a; color: #ffffff !important; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Reset your password</a>
</p>

<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">If you didn't request this, you can ignore this email. The link will expire in 6 hours.</p>
